Package org.rapidcontext.util

Interface HttpUtil.Status

Enclosing interface:
HttpUtil
public static interface HttpUtil.Status
The HTTP status codes as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0) and RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1).
